'''Muḥemmed''' (s [[taɛrabt]] محمّد - ''Muḥammad'') s teɣzi (''محمّد إبن عبد الله'', '''Muḥemmed ibn Ɛebdellah'''), ɣer inselmen, d imcagaɛ aneggaru n rrebi i d-yewwin ddin n [[Islam]]. Ilul di [[Mekka]] deg useggwas n 570 ass n 12 deg aggur [[Rabiɛ al awal]] ([[tafsut tamenzut]]) (20 ɣuct). Yemmut i [[Tamdint|Temdint]] deg useggwas n [[632]].

Ɣer wid yettamnen s yiwen rrebi, Muḥemmed yekfa timceggaɛt i d yebdan s [[Brahim]]. i tudert-is, yella yeqqar [[Leqran]] (awal-is i d-iceggeɛ rrebi s yiles n [[Ǧebril]]) i yemdukkal-is (ṣaḥaba). Leqran yettwaru deg asmi yemmut. Muḥemmed yeğğad daɣen [[Ssunna]], dayen yak i d-yenna neɣ i yexdem.

